html.htmlText:
Service animals aren’t pets, so there’s no need to add them here.

Traveling with an emotional support animal? Check out our accessibility policy.

Lounge by the heated pool at this expansive escape and gaze out at spectacular views over the sparkling waters of the Mediterranean sea and islands. Spread over 3 floors, this spacious getaway boasts an outdoor kitchen for alfresco evenings.

YOUR TRUST and SECURITY are our priority!

This exquisitely designed villa arranged over three floors with 7 bedrooms and 5 bathroom, is located in a beautiful hillside town of Orašac, just a 10 kilometers outside of the historical town of Dubrovnik. The villa is situated on a hillside, from each room and from the large terrace there are great views of Mediterranean Sea, its surrounding islands and lavish Dalmatian countryside. Located at the foot of the hillside is the Radisson Blue Spa and Resort.
In addition, enjoy and relax in our heated pool, outdoor kitchen and BBQ with seating area and terraces.

The villa’s many amenities include air conditioning and Sat-TV in each room, Netflix Tv show list , free WiFi, stereo player, safe box, dishwasher, microwave, kettle, coffee maker, washing machine, clothes dryer, iron, ironing board, baby cot on request, barbecue, private parking . Also included are welcome drink, cleaning & housekeeping once a week and swimming pool maintenance. There is no smoking inside the villa, only outside.

Guest access

On-site: the house is fully equipped to make your stay comfortable.
Property sleeps up to 14 people
Any extra guests will be charged 40eur per day.
Household appliances
Microwave, oven, coffee maker, toaster, dishwasher, washing machine, tumble dryer, refrigerators, freezer, stove, cooktop, kettle, iron and ironing board.
Indoor
Air conditionning in all the bedrooms, fireplace, central heating, hairdryer, bathtub, shower,Sat-TV,Netflix,Stereo,WIFI.
Supply of baby kit (cot with mattress , potty, changing mat, high chair, children's tableware, safety alarm for pool).
Services
Supply of bed linen and towels included.
FINAL CLEANING INCLUDED
Once a week cleaning and changing towels & linens .

Outside:

* Heated swimming pool of 25 m².

* Sunbathing area with 14 sunbeds

* Shower

* Laundry room

*Covered dinning room 14 people with kitchen and BBQ (wood).

*Outdoor furniture

*Free parking

This house was completely renovated in spring 2015.

I LIKE TO ENSURE YOUR VACATION STARTS OFF ON THE RIGHT FOOT.

I WILL PERSONALLY GREET YOU UPON ARRIVAL To THE VILLA.

ONCE YOU’VE HAD A CHANCE TO LEAVE YOUR BAGS AND GRAB A DRINK, I’M ALWAYS HAPPY TO GIVE YOU A QUICK WALK-THROUGH OF THE LOCAL AREA.

IF YOU’RE NOT UP TO IT, I’M EQUALLY HAPPY TO RUN YOU THROUGH A LIST OF KEY ATTRACTIONS AND CHEAT SHEETS FOR MAKING THE MOST OF YOUR STAY.

THROUGHOUT YOUR STAY,SHOULD YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS, NEED INFORMATION / ADVICE OR ANYTHING, I’M JUST A PHONE CALL AWAY OR FEEL FREE TO DROP ME AN EMAIL ANYTIME.

THERE WILL BE AN ADDITIONAL CHARGE SHOULD ADDITIONAL GUESTS BE ATTENDING THE WEDDING OR ANY OCCASION.

This sprawling property us perched on a scenic hillside in the popular town of Orašac, 10 kilometers outside of the historic Dubrovnik. Discover the tranquil Dalmatian countryside's vineyards and explore the region's pretty coastal villages.

Enjoy the amazing luxury accommodation, beautiful nature and quiet - away from crowded busy city life. Swimming in the swimming pool, rest at the terraces and balconies, make a barbecue... Go to the beach. Choose between pebble or rocky beaches in the vicinity of your villa or take a boat tour to the islands and visit sandy laguna beach at LOPUD island.
TRSTENO ARBORETUM
Take a trip to beautiful Trsteno Arboretum & Cove between Zaton & Slano. Now famous as a filming location for 'Game of Thrones' near 'Kings Landing' but a beautiful spot in its own right. Wonderful gardens led down to a stunning secret harbour with freshwater stream falling into the sea.
ORASAC is also known for its agro tourism so well worth taking a trip to one of the area's Konoba's to taste the delicious food and wine on offer. The Orasac Coast combines wonderful scenic views and pretty sea edge villages that are nearby to visit so get out and explore!
VELIKI ZALI BEACH
A wonderful beach to lose yourself for a day. A short drive up the coast from Orasac and you will come to the unspoilt bay of Zali. Crystal clear water, this is a favourite with the locals and with sunloungers, sun umbrellas, watersports on offer and a cozy cafe bar, you will find it hard to move once you've arrived...
The RADISSON SUN GARDENS is just down below in the bay with beaches, pools, water sports, a good selection of bars and restaurants, spa, and even a grocery shop.

Private terraced outdoor heated swimming pool with sunbeds all overlooking the sea.
Pool is not operational from 1st Nov to 1st April.
Rustic roofed pavilion outdoor kitchen in the pool area, with outdoor fireplace/BBQ pit, and dining outside for 14 people
Spacious pergola area covered with grapevines all with astonishing views, excellent for relaxation and unwinding
Parking place for three cars
Pool alarm child guard safety.
NETFLIX- TV show list

features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: 24-hour Safety Line
features.subtitle: If you ever feel unsafe, you’ll get priority access to specially-trained safety agents, day or night.
